            				</th>
            				<th width="5.882352941%" class="text-center" style="border-top:1px solid black;border-bottom:1px solid black;">
            					<strong style="color:white">.</strong>
            				</th>
            				<th width="5.882352941%" class="text-center" style="border-top:1px solid black;border-bottom:1px solid black;">
            					<strong style="color:white">.</strong>
            				</th>
            				<th width="5.882352941%" class="text-center" style="border-top:1px solid black;border-bottom:1px solid black;">
            					<strong>Price &amp; Amount in PKR</strong>
            				</th>
            				<th width="5.882352941%" class="text-center" style="border-top:1px solid black;border-bottom:1px solid black;">
            					<strong style="color:white">.</strong>
            				</th>
            				<th width="5.882352941%" class="text-left" style="border-top:1px solid black;border-bottom:1px solid black;border-right:1px solid black;">
            					<strong style="color:white">.</strong>
            				</th>
